<BaseLayout title="RPC & Game Comms · CS Notebook">
  <article class="space-y-6">
    <header>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-cyan mb-2">Networks / RPC & Game Comms</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">
        <Bilingual><span slot="zh">RPC 与游戏通信</span><span slot="en">RPC & Game Comms</span></Bilingual>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">RPC（远程过程调用）让客户端像调用本地函数一样调用远端服务。游戏行业广泛使用 RPC：<b>gRPC</b> 用于后端微服务（匹配/排行榜/背包），<b>Unreal Engine</b> 内置 Server/Client/NetMulticast 三种 RPC 复制机制，实时对战则常用<b>自定义 UDP RPC</b>。下方动画展示一次 RPC 调用的完整流程。</span>
          <span slot="en">RPC (Remote Procedure Call) lets a client invoke a remote service as if it were a local function. Games use RPC extensively: <b>gRPC</b> for backend microservices (matchmaking/leaderboard/inventory), <b>Unreal Engine</b> ships Server/Client/NetMulticast RPCs for replication, and real-time combat often uses <b>custom UDP RPC</b>. The animation below shows a full RPC call flow.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- 交互：RPC 调用流程时序图 -->
    <div class="glass p-5" data-viz="rpc-sequence">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <button id="rpc-play" class="btn btn-primary">
          <span data-ui="play" data-lang="zh">播放</span><span data-ui="play" data-lang="en">Play</span>
