    <!-- RPC 基本原理 -->
    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">RPC 基本原理</span><span slot="en">RPC Fundamentals</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">RPC 的核心是<b>透明化</b>远程调用：开发者写 <code>result = client.GetUser(id)</code>，底层自动完成「序列化 → 网络传输 → 反序列化 → 执行 → 返回」。关键组件：<b>Stub（桩）</b>在客户端伪装成本地函数，负责将参数<b>序列化（marshal）</b>为字节流；<b>Skeleton（骨架）</b>在服务端反序列化参数、调用真实实现、再序列化返回值。相比 REST API，RPC 通常用二进制协议（Protobuf/FlatBuffers），开销更低、类型更安全。</span><span slot="en">RPC's core is <b>transparency</b>: you write <code>result = client.GetUser(id)</code> and the machinery handles "serialize → transmit over network → deserialize → execute → return". Key components: the <b>Stub</b> masquerades as a local function on the client, <b>marshaling</b> parameters into a byte stream; the <b>Skeleton</b> on the server deserializes parameters, invokes the real implementation, and marshals the return value. Compared to REST APIs, RPC typically uses binary protocols (Protobuf/FlatBuffers) for lower overhead and stronger typing.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="text-ink-muted text-left"><tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">特性</span><span slot="en">Aspect</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4">REST API</th><th class="py-2 pr-4">RPC</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody class="text-ink">
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">传输协议</span><span slot="en">Transport</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4">HTTP/1.1 或 HTTP/2</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">TCP/UDP/HTTP/2</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">序列化</span><span slot="en">Serialization</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4">JSON（文本）</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">Protobuf/FlatBuffers（二进制）</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">类型安全</span><span slot="en">Type safety</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4">运行时校验</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">编译时生成</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">性能</span><span slot="en">Performance</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4">较高开销（文本解析）</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">低开销（二进制紧凑）</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">适用场景</span><span slot="en">Use case</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4">公开 API、Web 前端</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">微服务内部、游戏后端</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
