    <!-- 序列化格式对比 -->
    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">序列化格式对比</span><span slot="en">Serialization Format Comparison</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">RPC 的性能瓶颈往往在序列化。游戏常用三种格式：<b>Protobuf</b>（Google 出品，需编译生成代码，体积最小）；<b>FlatBuffers</b>（Google 出品，零拷贝反序列化，无需解析，适合游戏内实时通信）；<b>JSON</b>（人类可读，调试方便，但体积大、解析慢）。选型原则：后端微服务用 Protobuf，游戏内帧同步用 FlatBuffers，调试/配置用 JSON。</span><span slot="en">RPC performance bottleneck is often serialization. Three common formats in games: <b>Protobuf</b> (by Google, requires code generation, smallest payload); <b>FlatBuffers</b> (by Google, zero-copy deserialization, no parsing step—ideal for in-game real-time comms); <b>JSON</b> (human-readable, easy debugging, but large and slow). Rule of thumb: Protobuf for backend microservices, FlatBuffers for in-game frame sync, JSON for debugging/config.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
